-- Reliance MediaWorks Denies Report of Buying Majority Stake in Inox Leisure
-- Hemal Savai
-- 2010-07-30T06:04:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-30/reliance-mediaworks-denies-report-of-buying-majority-stake-in-inox-leisure.html

          
          
             Billionaire Anil Ambani’s Reliance
MediaWorks Ltd. denied an Economic Times report that said the
company has offered to buy a majority stake in Inox Leisure Ltd.  
 The company denies “any discussions by Reliance MediaWorks
or any offer by us to acquire any controlling stake in Inox,”
it said in an e-mailed statement in Mumbai today.   
